---
title: Chicken & Mushroom French Dip Sandwiches with Arugula, Herby Potatoes, Aioli & Au Jus
description: Dip dip hooray! Try this vegan twist on the classic hot sammie for a hearty dinner idea. Our chefs swapped out the traditional roast beef for meaty mushrooms, caramelized onion, and peppery arugula in a toasted baguette spread with vegan garlic aïoli. Add a side of crisp, ranch-spiced potato wedges, and for the grand finale: a rich, garlicky mushroom broth for dipping. Dunk, soak, swirl, repeat—this sumptuous French dip just can’t be beat.
